lead_paragraph: Robert Johnson had 17 points and seven rebounds and De'Ron Davis added 14 points to help No. 13 Indiana rout Southeast Missouri State 83-55 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: No. 13 Indiana Pulls Away From Southeast Missouri St. 83-55
